#. Tag: title
#: format.docbook:28
#, no-c-format
msgid "Spreadsheet Formatting"
msgstr "Formatiranje tabela"

#. Tag: title
#: format.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cell Format"
msgstr "Format ćelije"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:33
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To change the format and appearance of selected cell(s), row(s) or column(s) "
"use the <guimenuitem>Cell Format...</guimenuitem> option from the "
"<guimenu>Format</guimenu> menu or from the <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> "
"mouse button popup menu."
msgstr ""
"Da promijenite format i prikaz odabrane ćelije reda ili kolone "
"koristitie<guimenuitem>Format ćelije...</guimenuitem> opciju iz "
"<guimenu>Format</guimenu> menija ili skočni meni na <mousebutton>desna</"
"mousebutton> tipki miša."

#. Tag: phrase
#: format.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid "Right mouse button context menu."
msgstr "Kontekst meni u desnoj tipki miša."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will bring up the <guilabel>Cell Format</guilabel> dialog box which has "
"several tabbed pages:"
msgstr ""
"Ovo će prikazati <guilabel>Format ćelije</guilabel> okcir koji ima više "
"kartičnih stranica;:"

#. Tag: title
#: format.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid "Data Formats and Representation"
msgstr "Format podataka i prikaz"

#. Tag: phrase
#: format.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Data Format</guilabel> page."
msgstr "<guilabel>Format podataka</guilabel> stranica."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:62
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Data Format</guilabel> page of the <guilabel>Cell Format</"
"guilabel> dialog box lets you control how the values of cells are displayed."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Format podataka</guilabel> stranica iz <guilabel>Format ćelije</"
"guilabel> okvir dozvoljava kontrolu kako će biti vrijednosti u ćelijama "
"prikazane."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The top part of this page lets you select the format to be used when "
"displaying numeric values, dates or times. A <guilabel>Preview</guilabel> "
"pane allows you to see the effect of the new format."
msgstr ""
"Gornji dio ove stranice dozvoljava vam da odaberete format za korištenje pri "
"prikazu brojnih vrijednosti, datuma ili vremena. <guilabel>Pregled</"
"guilabel> panel dozvoljava vam da vidite efekat novog formata."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can set the same data format for a row or a column by selecting the row "
"or column and calling the <guilabel>Cell Format</guilabel> dialog with the "
"&RMB;."
msgstr ""
"Možete postaviti isti format podataka za red ili kolonu odabirom reda ili "
"kolone i pozivom  <guilabel>format ćelije</guilabel> okvir sa &RMB;."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:70
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can increase the precision decimal for any number in <guilabel>Generic</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Number</guilabel>, <guilabel>Percent</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Money</guilabel> or <guilabel>Scientific</guilabel> formats using "
"the <guiicon>Increase precision</guiicon> icon in the <guilabel>Format</"
"guilabel> toolbar:"
msgstr ""
"Možete povećati preciznost decimala za bilo koji broj u <guilabel>Generički</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Broj</guilabel>, <guilabel>Procenat</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Novac</guilabel> ili <guilabel>Naučni</guilabel> formati "
"korištenjem <guiicon>Povećaj preciznost</guiicon> ikone u <guilabel>Format</"
"guilabel> alatnoj traci:"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:76
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can decrease the precision decimal for any number in <guilabel>Generic</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Number</guilabel>, <guilabel>Percent</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Money</guilabel> or <guilabel>Scientific</guilabel> formats using "
"the <guiicon>Decrease precision</guiicon> icon in the <guilabel>Format</"
"guilabel> toolbar:"
msgstr ""
"Možete smanjiti preciznost decimala za bilo koji broj u <guilabel>Generički</"
"guilabel>, <guilabel>Broj</guilabel>, <guilabel>Procenat</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Novac</guilabel> ili <guilabel>Naučni</guilabel> formati "
"korištenjem <guiicon>Smanji preciznost</guiicon> ikone u <guilabel>Format</"
"guilabel> alatnoj traci:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "Generic"
msgstr "Generičko"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is the default format and &sheets; autodetects the actual data type "
"depending on the current cell data. By default, &sheets; right justifies "
"numbers, dates and times within a cell and left justifies anything else."
msgstr ""
"Ovo je zadani format i &sheets; automatski detektuje stvarni tip podataka "
"zavino od trenutnih podataa u ćeliji. Zadano &sheets; desno poravnjava "
"brojeve, datume i vremena unutar ćelije,a lijevo sve ostalo."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the <guilabel>Generic</guilabel> format does not suit you, you can change "
"to a specific format among the choices below."
msgstr ""
"Ako vam  <guilabel>Generički</guilabel> format ne odgovara možete ga "
"promijeniti u željeni format među ponuđenim ispod."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid "Number"
msgstr "Broj"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The number notation uses the notation you globally choose in "
"&systemsettings; in <menuchoice><guimenu>Locale</guimenu><guisubmenu>Country/"
"Region &amp; Language</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Numbers</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>. Numbers are right justified by default."
msgstr ""
"Zapis brojeva koristi zapis izabran u  &systemsettings; "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Locale</guimenu><guisubmenu>Country/Region &amp; "
"Language</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Numbers</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. "
"Brojevi su zadano desno poravnani."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid "Percent"
msgstr "Procenat"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:104
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you have a number in the current cell and you switch the cell format "
"from <guilabel>Generic</guilabel> to <guilabel>Percent</guilabel>, the "
"current cell number will be multiplied by 100."
msgstr ""
"Kada imate broj u trenutno ćeliji i promjenite njen format "
"<guilabel>Generički</guilabel> u <guilabel>Procenat</guilabel>, broj u "
"ćeliji se množi sa 100."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For example if you enter 2 and set the cell format to <guilabel>Percent</"
"guilabel>, the number will then be 200 %. Switching back to "
"<guilabel>Generic</guilabel> cell format will bring it back to 2."
msgstr ""
"Na primjer ako unesete 2 i postavite Format <guilabel>Procenat</guilabel>, "
"broj će biti 200%. Vraćanjem na <guilabel>Generički</guilabel> format ćelije "
"broj je 2."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also use the <guiicon>Percent</guiicon> icon in the "
"<guilabel>Format</guilabel> Toolbar:"
msgstr ""
"Možete koristiti <guiicon>Procenat</guiicon> ikonu u <guilabel>Format</"
"guilabel> alatnoj traci:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid "Money"
msgstr "Novac"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:118
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Money</guilabel> format converts your number into money "
"notation using the settings globally fixed in &systemsettings; in "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Locale</guimenu><guisubmenu>Country/Region &amp; "
"Language</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Money</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. The "
"currency symbol will be displayed and the precision will be the one set in "
"&systemsettings;."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Novac</guilabel> format pretvara vaš broj u novčani zapis "
"korištenjem globalnih postavki u &systemsettings; in "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Locale</guimenu><guisubmenu>Country/Region &amp; "
"Language</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Money</guimenuitem></menuchoice>.  Simbol "
"valute će biti prikazan i preciznost će biti ona postavljena u "
"&systemsettings;."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:122
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also use the <guiicon>Money Format</guiicon> icon in the "
"<guilabel>Format</guilabel> toolbar to set the cell formatting to look like "
"your current currency:"
msgstr ""
"Možete koristiti i  <guiicon>Format novca</guiicon> ikonu u  "
"<guilabel>Format</guilabel> alatnoj traci da podesite formatiranje ćelije u "
"vašoj trenutnoj valuti:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid "Scientific"
msgstr "Naučno"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:131
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Scientific</guilabel> format changes your number using the "
"scientific notation. For example, 0.0012 will be changed to 1.2E-03. Going "
"back using <guilabel>Generic</guilabel> cell format will display 0.0012 "
"again. The <guilabel>Generic</guilabel> cell data format does not keep "
"scientific notation so if you want this notation, you have to specify it "
"using this menu item."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Naučno</guilabel>format mijenja vaš broj korištenjem naučnog "
"zapisa. Na primjer, 0.0012 će biti promjenjeno u 1.2E-03. Povratak na "
"<guilabel>Generički</guilabel> format ćelija prikazaće se 0.0012 ponovo. "
"<guilabel>Generički</guilabel> format podataka u ćeliji ne sprema naučni "
"zapis ta da ako želite naučni zapis morate ga specificirati korištenjem ovog "
"menija."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:139
#, no-c-format
msgid "Fraction"
msgstr "Dio"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:140
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Fraction</guilabel> format changes your number into a "
"fraction. For example, 0.1 can be changed to 1/8, 2/16, 1/10, &etc; You "
"define the type of fraction by choosing it in the field on the right. If the "
"exact fraction is not possible in the fraction mode you choose, the nearest "
"closest match is chosen. For example: when we have 1.5 as number, we choose "
"<guilabel>Fraction</guilabel> and <guilabel>Sixteenths 1/16</guilabel> the "
"text displayed into cell is \"1 8/16\" which is an exact fraction. If you "
"have 1.4 as number in your cell and you choose <guilabel>Fraction</guilabel> "
"and <guilabel>Sixteenths 1/16</guilabel> then the cell will display \"1 "
"6/16\" which is the nearest closest Sixteenth fraction."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Dio</guilabel> format mijenja vaš broj u razlomak. Na primjer, 0.1 "
"može biti promjenjeno u 1/8, 2/16, 1/10, &itd; Vi definirate tip razlomka "
"korištenjem polja na desnoj strani. Ako tačan razlomak nije moguć u dio modu "
"birate, najbližu odgovarajuću vrijednost. Na primjer: kada imamo 1.5 kao "
"broj, biramo <guilabel>Dio</guilabel> i <guilabel>Šesnaestine</guilabel> "
"tekst u ćelijama je \"1 8/16\" koji je tačan razlomak. Ako imate 1.4 kao "
"broj u ćeliji i odaberete  <guilabel>Dio</guilabel> i <guilabel>Šesnaestine</"
"guilabel> onda će prikaz biti \"1 6/16\" što je najbliži šesnaesti dio."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid "Date"
msgstr "Datum"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:154
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To enter a date, you should enter it in one of the formats set in "
"&systemsettings; in <menuchoice><guimenu>Locale</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Country/Region &amp; Language</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Date "
"&amp; Time</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. There are two formats set here: the "
"date format and the short date format."
msgstr ""
"Za unos datuma, treba ga upisati u jednom od formata postavljenim u "
"postavkama sistema; u <menuchoice> <guimenu> Regionalne </guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu> Država / Regija &amp; Jezik </guisubmenu> <guimenuitem> Datum "
"&amp; Vrijeme </guimenuitem> </menuchoice>. Postoje dva formata postavljena "
"ovdje: format datuma i kratki format datuma."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:159
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A random natural number NN will be transformed in the date from 30st "
"December 1899 (which is 0) with the number of days NN added. For example if "
"you have a cell with 100 and you choose <guilabel>Date</guilabel> format, "
"\"1900-04-09\" will be displayed in the cell which is 100 days after 30st "
"December 1899. This starting date is two days early as it was a bug in Lotus "
"123 and then it stayed that way in Excel in order to keep compatibility. Few "
"people will need to calculate from 1st January 1900 anyway and adding 9 days "
"to 1st November 2000 for example will give you 10th November 2000 so all "
"normal calculations on dates are correct."
msgstr ""
"Slučajni prirodni broj NN će biti pretvoren u datum od 30st decembra 1899 "
"(što je 0) s brojem dana NN dodatih. Na primjer, ako imate ćeliju sa 100, a "
"vi odlučite <guilabel>Datum</guilabel> format, \"1900-04-09\" će biti "
"prikazan u ćeliji koja je 100 dana nakon 30. Decembra 1899.Datum početka je "
"dva dana ranije kao što je bio bug u Lotus 123, a onda je ostao na taj način "
"u Excelu kako bi se sačuvala kompatibilnost. Malo je ljudi koji će morati "
"izračunati od 1 januara 1900 ionako i dodati devet dana do 1. novembra 2000. "
"za primjer će vam dati 10. novembar 2000 pa su svi normalni proračuni za "
"datume tačni."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:168
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When a cell is in the <guilabel>Date</guilabel> format, you can drag this "
"cell down as you do with numbers and the next cells will also get dates, "
"each date being increased by one day."
msgstr ""
"Kada je ćelija u <guilabel>Datum</guilabel> formatu, možete prevući ovu "
"ćeliju dole kao i sa brojevima i slijedeće ćelije će također dobiti datume, "
"svaki uvećan za jedan dan."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:175
#, no-c-format
msgid "Time"
msgstr "Vrijeme"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This formats your cell content as a time. To enter a time, you should enter "
"it in the <guilabel>Time format</guilabel> set in &systemsettings; in "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Locale</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Country/Region &amp; "
"Language</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Date &amp; Time</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>. In the <guilabel>Cell Format</guilabel> dialog box you can set "
"how the time should be displayed by choosing one of the available time "
"format options. The default format is the system format set in "
"&systemsettings;. When the number in the cell does not make sense as a time, "
"&sheets; will display 00:00 in the global format you have in "
"&systemsettings;."
msgstr ""
"Ovo formatira sadržaj vaše ćelije kao vrijeme. Za unos vremena trebali biste "
"ga unijeti u <guilabel>Format vremena</guilabel> podešenog u "
"&systemsettings; u <menuchoice><guimenu>Locale</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Country/"
"Region &amp; Language</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Datum &amp; Vrijeme</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. U  <guilabel>Format ćelije</guilabel> dijaloškom "
"okviru možete podesiti kako bi vrijeme trebalo biti prikazano izborom jednog "
"od dva dostupna formata vremena. Zadani format je sistemski postavljen u "
"&systemsettings;. Kada broj u ćeliji nema smisla kad je u pitanju vrijeme  "
"&sheets; će prikazati 00:00 u globalnom formatu koji je podešen u  "
"&systemsettings;."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:189
#, no-c-format
msgid "Date and Time"
msgstr "Datum i vrijeme"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:190
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This formats your cell content as date and time. To enter a date and a time, "
"you should enter it in the <guilabel>Time format</guilabel> set in "
"&systemsettings; in <menuchoice><guimenu>Locale</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Country/Region &amp; Language</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Date "
"&amp; Time</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. In the <guilabel>Cell Format</"
"guilabel> dialog box you can set how the date and time should be displayed "
"by choosing one of the available date and time format options. The default "
"format is the system format set in &systemsettings;. When the number in the "
"cell does not make sense as a date and time, &sheets; will display 00:00 in "
"the global format you have in &systemsettings;."
msgstr ""
"Ovo formatira vaše ćelije kao datum i vrijeme. Da unesete dtum i vrijeme, "
"trebate to uraditi u <guilabel>Format vremena</guilabel> podešen u  "
"&systemsettings; u <menuchoice><guimenu>Locale</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Country/"
"Region &amp; Language</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Datum &amp; Vrijeme</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. U <guilabel>format ćelije</guilabel> okviru "
"možete podesiti kako bi datum i vrijeme trebali biti prikazani izborom jedng "
"od dostupnih datum i vrijeme formata. Zadani format je sistemski podešen u "
"&systemsettings;. Kada broj u ćeliji nema smisla kao datum i vrijeme, "
"&sheets; će prikazati 00:00 u globalnom formatu podešenom u &systemsettings;."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:203
#, no-c-format
msgid "Text"
msgstr "Tekst"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This formats your cell content as text. This can be useful if you want a "
"number treated as text instead as a number, for example for a ZIP code. "
"Setting a number as text format will left justify it. When numbers are "
"formatted as text, they cannot be used in calculations or formulas. It also "
"change the way the cell is justified."
msgstr ""
"Ovo formatira sadržaj ćelije kao tekst. Može biti korisno kada želite da "
"broj bude shvaćen kao tekst umjesto kao broj, npr. za poštanski broj. Kada "
"su brojevi u tekstualnom formatu, ne mogu se koristiti u izračunavanjima ili "
"formulama. Takođe se mijenja način na koji je sadržaj ćelije poravnat (tekst "
"se ravna lijevo, brojevi desno)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:212
#, no-c-format
msgid "Custom"
msgstr "Prilagođen"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:213
#, no-c-format
msgid "Does not work yet. To be enabled in the next release."
msgstr "Još ne radi. Biće omogućeno u slijedećoj verziji."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:218
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The lower part of the <guilabel>Data Format</guilabel> page lets you add a "
"<guilabel>Prefix:</guilabel> such as a $ symbol at the start of each item or "
"a <guilabel>Postfix:</guilabel> such as $HK to the end. You can also control "
"how many digits are displayed after the decimal point for numeric values, "
"whether positive values are displayed with a leading + sign and whether "
"negative values are shown in red."
msgstr ""
"Donji dio stranice <guilabel>Format datuma</guilabel> dozvoljava vam da "
"dodate <guilabel>Prefiks:</guilabel> kao $ simbol na početak svake stavke "
"ili   <guilabel>Postfiks:</guilabel> kao $HK na kraj. Također možete "
"kontrolisati broj cifara koje će biti prikazane nakon decimalnog  zareza za "
"numeričke vrijednosti, da li ce biti prikazane pozitivne vrijednosti sa "
"znakom + ili negativne vrijednosti crvenim slovima."

#. Tag: title
#: format.docbook:228
#, no-c-format
msgid "Fonts and Text Settings"
msgstr "Postavke fonta i teksta"

#. Tag: phrase
#: format.docbook:235
#, no-c-format
msgid "Font page."
msgstr "Stranica fonta."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:239
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Font</guilabel> page lets you select the font family, "
"<guilabel>Style:</guilabel>, <guilabel>Size:</guilabel>, <guilabel>Weight:</"
"guilabel> and <guilabel>Color:</guilabel> for the current cell, including "
"some additional options like underlined or striked out text. The lower part "
"of the page gives a <guilabel>Preview</guilabel> of the selected text format."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Font</guilabel> stranica vam dozvoljava da odaberete vrstu fonta,, "
"<guilabel>Stil:</guilabel>, <guilabel>Veličinu:</guilabel>, <guilabel>Težinu:"
"</guilabel> i <guilabel>Boju:</guilabel> za trenutnu opciju, uključujući i "
"dodatne opcije kao podvučen ili precrtan tekst. donji dio stranice omogućava "
"<guilabel>Pregled</guilabel> odabranog formata teksta."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:244
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The default font is set for all cells in the <menuchoice><guimenu>Format</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Style Manager</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu with the "
"currently used style."
msgstr ""
"Zadani font je postavljen za sve ćelije u <menuchoice><guimenu>Format</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Upravitelj stilom</guimenuitem></menuchoice> meniju sa "
"trenutno korištenim stilom."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:255
#, no-c-format
msgid "Style:"
msgstr "Izgled:"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:256
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose the style for your font for the currently selected cells. When you "
"select several cells with different styles, the displayed style is set to "
"<guilabel>Varying (No Change)</guilabel> and leaving it that way will keep "
"all your current style settings for each cell. Changing to <guilabel>Roman</"
"guilabel> for example will change all the selected cells style text to "
"<guilabel>Roman</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Odaberite stil za vaš font za trenutno odabrane ćelije. Kada odaberete "
"nekoliko ćelija s različitim stilovima, prikazan je stil "
"<guilabel>Varira(Bez promjena)</guilabel> i ako ga ostavite tako trenutne "
"postavke stila za svaku ćeliju biće iste. Promjena u <guilabel>Roman</"
"guilabel> na primjer će promjeniti stil odabranih ćelija  u <guilabel>Roman</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:265
#, no-c-format
msgid "Size:"
msgstr "Veličina:"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:266
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose the size for your font for the currently selected cells. When you "
"select several cells with different sizes, the displayed size is set to "
"<guilabel> </guilabel> (no number written) and leaving it that way will keep "
"all your current size settings for each cell. Changing to <guilabel>14</"
"guilabel> for example will change all the selected cells font size to "
"<guilabel>14</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Odaberite veličinu fonta za trenutno odabrane ćelije. Kada odaberete "
"nekoliko ćelija sa različitim veličinama fonta, prikazana veličina je "
"<guilabel> </guilabel>  (bez prikazanog broja) i ako ga ostavite tako "
"zadržaćete sve trenutne postavke veličine fonta za svaku ćeliju. Ako "
"promjenite u <guilabel>14</guilabel> na primjer promjeniće veličinu fonta u "
"odabranim ćelijana na <guilabel>14</guilabel>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:275
#, no-c-format
msgid "Weight:"
msgstr "Težina:"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:276
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose the weight for your font for the currently selected cells. When you "
"select several cells with different font weight, the displayed weight is set "
"to <guilabel>Varying (No Change)</guilabel> and leaving it that way will "
"keep all your current weight settings for each cell. Changing to "
"<guilabel>Bold</guilabel> for example will change all the selected cells "
"font weight to <guilabel>Bold</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Izaberite debljinu fonta za trenutno izabrane ćelije. Kada odaberete "
"nekoliko ćelija sa različitom debljinom fonta , prikazana vrijednost će biti "
"<guilabel>Varira (Bez promjena)</guilabel> i ako je ostavite tako zadržaće "
"trenutne postavke debljine fonta za sve ćelije. Ako promjenite u "
"<guilabel>Podebljano</guilabel> na primjer promjniće debljinu fonta u svim "
"odabranim ćelijama u <guilabel>Podebljano</guilabel>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:285
#, no-c-format
msgid "Color:"
msgstr "Boja:"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:286
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Choose the color for the currently selected cells' text. Clicking on the "
"color bar will bring you the standard KDE <guilabel>Select Color</guilabel> "
"dialog where you will be able to choose the new color."
msgstr ""
"Izaberite boju teksta u trenutno odabranim ćelijama. Pritiskom na traku sa "
"bojama biće prikazan standardni KDE <guilabel>Odaberi boju</guilabel> okvir, "
"gdje možete odabrati novu boju."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:292
#, no-c-format
msgid "Underline"
msgstr "Podvučeno"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:293
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Underlines the currently selected cells' text if checked. This is not "
"checked per default."
msgstr ""
"Podvlači trenutno odabrane ćelije ako je označen. Zadano nije označeno."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:299
#, no-c-format
msgid "Strike out"
msgstr "Precrtano"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:300
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will strike out the currently selected cells' text if this is checked. "
"This is not checked per default."
msgstr ""
"Ovo će precrtati trenutno odabrane ćelije ako je označen. Zadano nije "
"označeno."

#. Tag: title
#: format.docbook:309
#, no-c-format
msgid "Text Position and Rotation"
msgstr "Pozicija teksta i rotacija"

#. Tag: phrase
#: format.docbook:316
#, no-c-format
msgid "Position page."
msgstr "Stranica pozicije."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:320
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"From the <guilabel>Position</guilabel> page you can control the position of "
"text within a cell by making suitable selections in the <guilabel>Horizontal "
"</guilabel> and <guilabel>Vertical</guilabel> areas or by setting the "
"<guilabel>Indent</guilabel> value. You can also choose to have the text "
"appear vertically rather than horizontally, or even at an angle."
msgstr ""
"Iz <guilabel>Pozicija</guilabel> stranice možete kontrolisati poziciju "
"teksta unutar ćelije biranjem u  <guilabel>Vodoravno</guilabel> i "
"<guilabel>Uspravno</guilabel> područjima ili postavljanjem "
"<guilabel>Uvučeno</guilabel> vrijednosti. Možete odabrati da se tekst pojavi "
"uspravno umjesto vodoravno, ili čak pod uglom."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:328
#, no-c-format
msgid "Horizontal"
msgstr "Vodoravno"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:329
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the content position horizontally in the cell. <guilabel>Standard</"
"guilabel> is default and is set from the data format you choose. "
"<guilabel>Left</guilabel> means the content will be displayed on the left of "
"the cell. <guilabel>Center</guilabel> means the content will be in the "
"center horizontally in the cell. <guilabel>Right</guilabel> means the "
"content of the cell will be displayed on the right of the cell."
msgstr ""
"Posavite poziciju sadržaja vodoravno u ćeliji. <guilabel>Standardno</"
"guilabel> je zadano i postavljeno za podatke koje izaberete. "
"<guilabel>Lijevo</guilabel> znači da će sadržaj biti prikazan u lijevoj "
"strani ćelije. <guilabel>Centralno</guilabel> znači da će sadržaj biti na "
"sredini vodoravno u ćeliji. <guilabel>Desno</guilabel> znači da će sadržaj "
"biti prikazan u desnoj strani ćelije."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:338
#, no-c-format
msgid "Vertical"
msgstr "Uspravno"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:339
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the content position vertically in the cell. <guilabel>Top</guilabel> "
"means the content will be displayed on top of the cell. <guilabel>Middle</"
"guilabel> means the content will be in the middle vertically in the cell. "
"<guilabel>Bottom</guilabel> means the content of the cell will be displayed "
"at the bottom of the cell."
msgstr ""
"Postavite poziciju sadržaja uspravno u ćeliji. <guilabel>Vrh</guilabel> "
"znači da će sadržaj biti prikazan na vrhu ćelije. <guilabel>Sredina</"
"guilabel> znači da će sadržaj biti prikazan na sredini uspravno u ćeliji. "
"<guilabel>Dno</guilabel> znači da će sadržaj biti prikazan na dnu ćelije."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:347
#, no-c-format
msgid "Text Option"
msgstr "Opcije teksta"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:348
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is only available when the rotation is 0°. <guilabel>Wrap text</"
"guilabel> wraps the text so it fits in the previous cell size. If this is "
"not checked, the text will stay on one line."
msgstr ""
"Ovo je dostupno samo kad je rotacija 0°. <guilabel>Prelomi tekst</guilabel> "
"prelama tekst tako da stane u prethodnu veličinu ćelije. Ako je odznačeno "
"tekst će ostati u jednoj liniji."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:351
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Vertical text</guilabel> puts your text vertically."
msgstr "<guilabel>Tekst uspravno</guilabel> postavlja vaš tekst uspravno."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:355
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rotation"
msgstr "Rotacija"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:356
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Your text will appear oriented in the angle you set here. Positive values "
"will move it counter-clockwise and negative values will move it clockwise."
msgstr ""
"Tekst će biti zaokrenut za ugao koji ovdje postavite. Pozitivne vrijednosti "
"će okretati suprotno smjeru kazaljke na satu, a negativne u smjeru."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:362
#, no-c-format
msgid "Merge Cells"
msgstr "Spoji Ćelije"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:363
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When checked, this has the same effect as <menuchoice><guimenu>Format</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Merge Cells</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. You need to "
"have at least two consecutive cells selected. Those consecutive cells are "
"then merged into a bigger one."
msgstr ""
"Kad je označeno ima isti efekat kao <menuchoice><guimenu>Format</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Spoji ćelije</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Morate "
"odabrati bar dvije ćelije. Te ćelije su zatim spojene u jednu veću."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:368
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When a merged cell is selected and when you uncheck this, then all cells "
"come back to their original size as before the merging. It has the same "
"effect as <menuchoice><guimenu>Format</guimenu><guimenuitem>Dissociate "
"Cells</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Kada je odabrana spojena ćelija i kada odznačite ovo, sve ćelije se vraćaju "
"u prvobitnu veličinu prije spajanja. Ima isti efekat kao "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Format</guimenu><guimenuitem>Razdvoji ćelije</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:375
#, no-c-format
msgid "Indent"
msgstr "Uvuci"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:376
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set the amount of indent that will be used in the cell when you choose the "
"<guilabel>Increase Indent</guilabel>/<guilabel>Decrease Indent</guilabel> "
"actions from the toolbar. These actions are not enabled by default in the "
"toolbar."
msgstr ""
"Odaberite količinu sadržaja koja će biti korištena u ćeliji kada odaberete "
"<guilabel>Povećaj sadržaj</guilabel>/<guilabel>Smanji sadržaj</guilabel> "
"akcije iz alatne trake. Ove akcije nisu omogućene zadano u alatnoj traci."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:382
#, no-c-format
msgid "Size of Cell"
msgstr "Veličina ćelije"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:383
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You set here the size of the cell, either a custom width and height or "
"choose the default width and height."
msgstr ""
"Ovdje podesite veličinu ćelije, ili željenu širinu i visinu ćelije ili "
"izaberite zadanu širinu i visinu."

#. Tag: title
#: format.docbook:391
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cell Border"
msgstr "Okvir ćelije"

#. Tag: phrase
#: format.docbook:398
#, no-c-format
msgid "Border page."
msgstr "Okvir stranice."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:402
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Border</guilabel> page lets you set the appearance of the cell "
"borders. If you have selected more than one cell you can apply different "
"styles to the borders between the cells and that surrounding the selected "
"area."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Okvir</guilabel> stranica vam dozvoljava da postavite izgled "
"okvira ćelije. Ako ste odabrali više od jedne ćelije možete podesiti "
"različit stil okvira tih ćelija i ćelija koje se nalaze u njihovoj okolini."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:406
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"First select the pattern and color from the <guilabel>Pattern</guilabel> "
"section of the <guilabel>Border</guilabel> page then apply that to different "
"parts of the border by clicking on the appropriate button in the "
"<guilabel>Border</guilabel> section, or on one of the <guilabel>Preselect </"
"guilabel> buttons. The left hand button in the <guilabel>Preselect </"
"guilabel> section will clear any previously applied border(s). Note that you "
"can also add a diagonal strike-through line to the cell(s)."
msgstr ""
"Prvo odaberite uzorak i boju <guilabel>Uzorak</guilabel> dio u "
"<guilabel>Okvir</guilabel> stranici i onda to primjeniti na različite "
"dijelove okvira pritiskom na odgovarajuću  tipku u <guilabel>Okvir</"
"guilabel> dijelu ili neku od <guilabel>Ponovo odaberi </guilabel> tipki. "
"Lijeva tipka u <guilabel>Ponovo odaberi </guilabel> odjeljku će obrisati "
"svaki prethodno izabrani okvir. Primjetite da možete odabrati da dodate "
"dijagonalno prikazane linije u ćeliji."

#. Tag: title
#: format.docbook:415
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cell Background"
msgstr "Pozadina ćelije"

#. Tag: phrase
#: format.docbook:422
#, no-c-format
msgid "Background page."
msgstr "Pozadina stranice."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:426
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The cell background pattern and color can be selected from the "
"<guilabel>Background</guilabel> page."
msgstr ""
"Uzorak za pozadinu ćelije i boju može biti odabran u <guilabel>Pozadina</"
"guilabel> stranici."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:428
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Simply choose a desired <guilabel>Pattern</guilabel>, then select the "
"pattern <guilabel>Color</guilabel> and the <guilabel>Background color</"
"guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Jednostavno odaberite željeni <guilabel>Uzorak</guilabel>, a zatim odaberite "
"uzorak <guilabel>Boje</guilabel> i <guilabel>Boju pozadine</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:430
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At the bottom of this page you can see a <guilabel>Preview</guilabel> of the "
"configured cell background."
msgstr ""
"Na dnu ove stranice možete vidjeti <guilabel>Prikaz</guilabel> podešavanja "
"pozadine ćelije."

#. Tag: title
#: format.docbook:434
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cell Protection"
msgstr "Zaštita ćelije"

#. Tag: phrase
#: format.docbook:441
#, no-c-format
msgid "Cell protection page."
msgstr "Stranica za zaštitu ćelije."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:445
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can change the way the content of a cell is protected in the "
"<guilabel>Cell Protection</guilabel> page."
msgstr ""
"Možete odabrati način na koji je sadržaj ćelije zaštićen u <guilabel>Zaštita "
"ćelije</guilabel> stranici."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:447
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All cells are protected by default (that means cell content cannot be "
"changed) and for the cell protection to be active you also need to protect "
"the sheet using the <menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Protect "
"Sheet...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu and to provide a password. You can "
"also hide the cell formula in order to protect the way you calculate the "
"formula. This also needs to enable sheet protection to work. You can hide "
"the cell content with <guilabel>Hide all</guilabel> and again this needs "
"sheet protection. You can learn more about all these settings in the <link "
"linkend=\"protection\">Advanced &sheets; chapter, Protection section</link>."
msgstr ""
"Sve ćelije su zadano zaštićene (to znači da se sadržaj ćelija ne može "
"mijenjati) i da bi zaštita ćelija bila aktivirana morate zaštititi i list "
"korištenjem <menuchoice><guimenu>Alati</guimenu><guimenuitem>Zaštiti list..."
"</guimenuitem></menuchoice>  menija i osigurati šifru. Možete također "
"sakriti formulu u ćeliji u cilju zaštite načina na koji računate formulu. "
"Ovo također treba omogućiti da radi zaštita lista. Sadržaj ćelije možete "
"sakriti sa <guilabel>Sakrij sve</guilabel> i ovo treba zaštitu lista. Više o "
"ovim postavkama možete naučiti na <link linkend=\"protection\">Napredno "
"&sheets; poglavlje, Odjeljak za zaštitu</link>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:460
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hide all"
msgstr "Sakrij sve"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:461
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This hides the cell content and works only when the sheet is protected which "
"means that changing the <guilabel>Hide all</guilabel> attribute of a cell "
"has no effect unless the sheet is protected. Whether the cell itself is "
"protected or not does not matter."
msgstr ""
"Ovo sakriva sadržaj ćelije i radi samo kad je list zaštićen što znači "
"promjenu <guilabel>Sakrij sve</guilabel> atributa ćelije i nema efekat ako "
"list nije zaštićen. Da li je ćelija zaštićena sama od sebe ili ne nije bitno."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:465
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When <guilabel>Hide all</guilabel> is selected, <guilabel>Protected</"
"guilabel> and <guilabel>Hide formula</guilabel> are disabled as when the "
"sheet is protected <guilabel>Hide all</guilabel> hides the cell content and "
"the formula and thus masks and protects the cell content."
msgstr ""
"Kada je <guilabel>Sakrij sve</guilabel> odabrano, <guilabel>Zaštita</"
"guilabel> i <guilabel>Sakrij formulu</guilabel> su onemogućene kao i kad je "
"list zaštićen <guilabel>Sakrij sve</guilabel> sakriva sav sadržaj ćelije i "
"formulu i maske i štiti sadržaj ćelije."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:472
#, no-c-format
msgid "Protected"
msgstr "Zaštićeno"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:473
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If checked, the cell content will be protected. This is the default "
"behaviour. You need to protect the whole sheet using the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Protect Sheet...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu for this individual cell protection to work. "
"When a cell is protected, its content cannot be changed."
msgstr ""
"Ako je označeno, sadržaj ćelije će biti zaštićen. Ovo je zadano ponašanje. "
"Trebate zaštititi cijeli listi korištenjem  <menuchoice><guimenu>alati</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Zaštiti list...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> meni da bi "
"individualna zaštita ćelije radila. Kada je ćelija zaštićena, sadržaj ne "
"može biti izmjenjen."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:481
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hide formula"
msgstr "Sakrij formulu"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:482
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When this is checked, the cell is still visible. However, its contents do "
"not appear in the <guilabel>Formula</guilabel> bar. Hiding formula is only "
"working for cells that contain formulae so the user cannot view the formula. "
"And the sheet must be protected for this to work."
msgstr ""
"Kada je ovo označeno ćelija je i dalje vidljiva. Ali njen sadržaj se ne "
"pojavljuje u <guilabel>Formula</guilabel> traci. Sakrivanje formule samo "
"radi za ćelije koje sadrže formulu tako da korisnik ne može vidjeti formulu. "
"Da bi ovo radilo list mora biti zaštićen."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:490
#, no-c-format
msgid "Do not print text"
msgstr "Ne ispisuj tekst"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:491
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you check <guilabel>Do not print text</guilabel> then the text in the "
"cell will not be printed. This is unchecked per default which means that the "
"cell text will always be printed by default."
msgstr ""
"Ako označite <guilabel>Ne prikazuj tekst</guilabel> tekst u ćeliji neće biti "
"prikazan. Ovo je zadano odznačeno što znači da će zadano tekst u ćelijama "
"uvijek biti prikazan."

#. Tag: title
#: format.docbook:501
#, no-c-format
msgid "Conditional Cell Attributes"
msgstr "Uslovni atributi ćelije"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:502
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can make the appearance of a cell change according to the value it "
"contains, useful perhaps if you are using &sheets; to keep track of your "
"household expenses and want to highlight any item greater than, say, one "
"thousand dollars."
msgstr ""
"Možete podesiti da se ozgled ćelije mijenja u skladu sa vrijednošću koju "
"sadrži, korisno ako koristite  &sheets; da pratite troškove domaćinstva i "
"želite istaći neku stavku skuplju od recimo hiljadu dolara."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:506
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To do this select the cell(s) then choose <guimenuitem>Conditional Styles..."
"</guimenuitem> from the <guimenu>Format</guimenu> menu. This will bring up "
"the <guilabel>Conditional Styles</guilabel> dialog box where you can make "
"the font type and color of a cell change when the value meets one or more "
"conditions. Note that the second and third conditions only apply if the "
"previous condition(s) are not met."
msgstr ""
"Da uradite ovo odaberite ćelije, a zatim <guimenuitem>Uslovni stilovi...</"
"guimenuitem> iz <guimenu>Format</guimenu> menija. Ovo će prikazati "
"<guilabel>Uslovni stilovi</guilabel> okvi gdje možete odabrati tip fonta i "
"boju u koju se promijeni ćelija kada su ispunjeni određeni uslovi. "
"Primjetite da se primjenjuju drugi i treći uslov samo ako prethodni nisu "
"ispunjeni."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:512
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use <menuchoice><guisubmenu>Clear</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Conditional "
"Styles</guimenuitem></menuchoice> from the <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> menu to "
"clear any conditional attributes from selected cells."
msgstr ""
"Koristite <menuchoice><guisubmenu>Očisti</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Uslovni "
"stilovi </guimenuitem></menuchoice> iz <guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> menija da "
"očistite uslovne atribute iz odabranih ćelija."

#. Tag: title
#: format.docbook:518
#, no-c-format
msgid "Changing Cell Sizes"
msgstr "Promjena veličina ćelije"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:519
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Position</guilabel> page in the <guilabel>Cell Format</"
"guilabel> dialog lets you alter the size of the selected cell(s). Note that "
"changing the height of a single cell will change the height for all cells in "
"that row, similarly changing the width will affect the entire column."
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Pozicija</guilabel> stranica u <guilabel>Format ćelije</guilabel> "
"okviru dozvoljava da povećate veličinu odabranih ćelija. Primjetite da "
"promjena visine jedne ćelije mijenja visinu svih ćelija u redu, slično je i "
"sa širinom, utjecaće na sve ćelije u koloni."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:523
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also select the row(s) or column(s) to be changed then select "
"<guimenuitem>Resize Row...</guimenuitem> or <guimenuitem>Resize Column...</"
"guimenuitem> from the <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> mouse button pop up "
"menu or from the <menuchoice><guimenu>Format</guimenu><guisubmenu>Row</"
"guisubmenu> </menuchoice> or <menuchoice><guimenu>Format</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu> Column</guisubmenu></menuchoice> menu."
msgstr ""
"Možete odabrati redove ili kolone koje želite promijenjiti, odaberite "
"<guimenuitem>Promjeni velićinu reda...</guimenuitem> ili "
"<guimenuitem>Promjeni veličinu kolone...</guimenuitem> iz "
"<mousebutton>desni</mousebutton> tipke miša menija ili iz "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Format</guimenu><guisubmenu>Red</guisubmenu> </"
"menuchoice> ili <menuchoice><guimenu>Format</guimenu><guisubmenu> Kolona</"
"guisubmenu></menuchoice> menija."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:529
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you move the mouse cursor so that its tip is over the line between two of "
"the row numbers at the left of &sheets;'s window the cursor will change to "
"show two parallel lines each with a short arrow headed line coming from it. "
"When the cursor is in this state you can hold the <mousebutton>left </"
"mousebutton> mouse button down and drag the border between the two rows, "
"changing the height of the upper row. A similar technique can be used to "
"change the width of a column."
msgstr ""
"Ako pomjerite pokazivač miša tako da je njegov vrh iznad linije između broja "
"reda na lijevoj strani prozora &sheets;-a pokazivač će se promijeniti da "
"pokazuje dvije paralelne linije obje sa kratkom strelicom koja izlazi iz "
"nje. Kada je kursor u stanju kad možete držati <mousebutton>lijevu </"
"mousebutton> tipku miša i previći ovir između dva reda, promjenom visine "
"gornjeg reda. Slična tehnika može biti korištena da se promijeni širina "
"kolone."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:537
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To set the row height or column width to the minimum needed to display the "
"contents, select the whole row or column, and click with the &RMB; on the "
"row or column label. In the menu which appears, select <guimenuitem>Adjust "
"Row</guimenuitem> or <guimenuitem>Adjust Column</guimenuitem>. The row or "
"column will resize to the minimum necessary. You can also select a single "
"cell or range of cells, and click <guimenuitem>Adjust Row &amp; Column</"
"guimenuitem> from either the &RMB; popup menu or the <guimenu>Format</"
"guimenu> menu."
msgstr ""
"Da podesite visinu reda i širinu kolone na minimum koji je potreban za "
"prikaz sadržaja, odaberite red ili kolonu, i pritisnite &RMB; na red ili "
"kolonu. U meniju koji se pojavi, odaberite <guimenuitem>Prilagodi red</"
"guimenuitem> ili <guimenuitem>Prilagodi kolonu</guimenuitem>. Red i kolona "
"će promijeniti veličinu na minimalnu potrebnu. Možete odabrati jednu čeliju "
"ili dio ćelija i pritisnuti <guimenuitem>Prilagodi red &amp; kolonu</"
"guimenuitem> ili iz &RMB; skočnog menija ili <guimenu>Format</guimenu> "
"menija."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:546
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can make a number of adjacent rows or columns the same size by selecting "
"them then choosing <menuchoice><guimenu>Format</guimenu><guisubmenu> Row</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Equalize Row</guimenuitem></menuchoice> or "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Format</guimenu><guisubmenu>Column</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Equalize Column</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Možete napraviti da se redovi i kolone prilagode na istu veličinu ako ih "
"odaberete i odaberete <menuchoice><guimenu>Format</guimenu><guisubmenu>Red</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Izjednači red</guimenuitem></menuchoice> ili "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Format</guimenu><guisubmenu>Kolona</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Izjednači kolonu</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: title
#: format.docbook:555
#, no-c-format
msgid "Merging Cells"
msgstr "Spajanje ćelija"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:556
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is often convenient to have one cell that spreads across two or more "
"columns or down more than one row. This can be done by merging two or more "
"cells into one. Select the cells to be merged than choose "
"<menuchoice><guimenu> Format</guimenu><guimenuitem>Merge Cells</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Često je slučaj da se jedna ćelija širi preko dvije ili više kolona ili više "
"od jednog reda. Ovo se može uraditi spajanjem dvije ili više ćelija u jednu. "
"Odaberite ćelije koje želite spojiti i odaberite <menuchoice><guimenu> "
"Format</guimenu><guimenuitem>Spoji ćelije</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:560
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To reverse this process, select the merged cell then choose <guimenuitem> "
"Dissociate Cells</guimenuitem> from the <guimenu>Format</guimenu> menu."
msgstr ""
"Da poništite ovaj proces, odaberite spojene ćelije i odaberite <guimenuitem> "
"Razdvoji ćelije</guimenuitem> iz <guimenu>Format</guimenu> menija."

#. Tag: title
#: format.docbook:565
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hiding Rows and Columns"
msgstr "Sakrivanje redova i kolona"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:566
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A finished spreadsheet can often be made to look more attractive by hiding "
"the cells containing intermediate calculations so that only the important "
"data input and result areas are shown."
msgstr ""
"Završena tabela može često izgledati privalčnije ako sakrijete ćelije koje "
"sadrže međuprodukte tako da su prikazani bitni ulazni podaci i rezultati."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:569
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In &sheets; you can hide selected rows or columns by using the "
"<guimenuitem>Hide Rows</guimenuitem> and <guimenuitem>Hide Columns</"
"guimenuitem> options from the <menuchoice><guimenu>Format</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Row</guisubmenu></menuchoice>, <menuchoice><guimenu>Format </"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Column</guisubmenu></menuchoice> or <mousebutton>right</"
"mousebutton> mouse button menus. Hidden rows and columns are not displayed "
"on the screen or included in a print out."
msgstr ""
"U  &sheets; možete sakriti odabrane redove i kolone korištenjem "
"<guimenuitem>Sakrij redove</guimenuitem> i <guimenuitem>Sakrij kolone</"
"guimenuitem> opcije iz <menuchoice><guimenu>Format</guimenu> "
"<guisubmenu>Red</guisubmenu></menuchoice>, <menuchoice><guimenu>Format </"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Kolona</guisubmenu></menuchoice> ili <mousebutton>desni</"
"mousebutton> klik miša menija. Sakriveni redovi i kolone nisu prikazane na "
"ekranu i uključene u printanje."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:576
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Hiding cells in this way also makes them slightly less prone to accidental "
"change."
msgstr ""
"Sakrivanje ćelija na ovaj način može ih sačuvati od slučajnih promijena."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:578
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To un-hide a row or column select <menuchoice><guisubmenu>Row </"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Show Rows...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> or "
"<menuchoice><guisubmenu>Column</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Show Columns...</"
"guimenuitem> </menuchoice> from the <guimenu>Format</guimenu> menu. In the "
"dialog box which appears, you can select any number of rows to show."
msgstr ""
"Da poništite sakrivanje reda ili kolone odaberite "
"<menuchoice><guisubmenu>Red </guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Prikaži red...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> ili <menuchoice><guisubmenu>Kolona</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Prikaži kolone...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> iz "
"<guimenu>Format</guimenu> menija. U okviru koji se pojavi , možete odabrati "
"broj redova za prikaz."

#. Tag: title
#: format.docbook:587
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sheet properties"
msgstr "Osobine lista"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:588
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can access the current sheet properties either by right clicking on the "
"sheet tab and choosing <guilabel>Sheet Properties</guilabel> or by using the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Format</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Sheet</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Sheet Properties</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu. "
"Please note that you can only access the <guilabel>Sheet Properties</"
"guilabel> when the document or the sheet is not protected."
msgstr ""
"Možete pristupiti osobinama trenutnog lista ili desnim klikom na karticu "
"lista i izborom <guilabel>Osobine lista</guilabel> ili korištenjem "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Format</guimenu> <guisubmenu>List</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Osobine lista</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menija. "
"Obratite pažnju da možete samo pristupiti <guilabel>Osobinama lista</"
"guilabel> kada dokument ili list nisu zaštićeni."

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:595
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can set different properties that will be valid in the current sheet. "
"Clicking on <guibutton>OK</guibutton> will validate your changes and "
"<guibutton>Defaults</guibutton> will bring back the default settings."
msgstr ""
"Možete odbrati druge osobine koje će vrijediti u trenutnom listu. Pritiskom "
"na <guibutton>OK</guibutton> potvrdićete promjene <guibutton>Zadano</"
"guibutton> će vratiti na zadane postavke."

#. Tag: phrase
#: format.docbook:604
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sheet Properties dialog."
msgstr "Okvir sa osobinama lista."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:610
#, no-c-format
msgid "Layout direction:"
msgstr "Smjer rasporeda:"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:611
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Let you choose the sheet orientation. Default is that the first column of "
"the sheet is on the left. If you choose <guilabel>Right to Left</guilabel>, "
"then the first column will be on the right and the others added from right "
"to left."
msgstr ""
"Omogućava vam izbor orijentacije lista. ZAdano je da je prva kolona lista "
"lijevo. Ako odaberete <guilabel>Desno prema lijevo</guilabel>, onda će prva "
"kolona biti desno, a ostale dodate s desna na lijevo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:617
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hide zero"
msgstr "Sakrij nulu"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:618
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this box is checked any cell containing the value zero will appear blank."
msgstr ""
"Kada je ova kućica popunjena, svaka ćelija koja sadrži nulu biće prikazana "
"kao prazna."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:623
#, no-c-format
msgid "Automatic recalculation"
msgstr "Automatsko ponovno izračunavanje"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:624
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This setting controls whether formulae are recalculated automatically when "
"the value of any cell they refer to changes."
msgstr ""
"Ova postavka kontroliše da li se formule automatski preračunavaju kada se "
"promijeni vrijednost bilo koje ćelije od kojih formula zavisi."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:629
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show column as numbers"
msgstr "Prikaži kolone kao brojeve"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:630
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this box is checked the column headings will show as numbers rather than "
"as letters. Letters are default."
msgstr ""
"Ako je ova kućica popunjena, zaglavlja kolona biće prikazana kao brojevi "
"umjesto kao slova. Podrazumijevana su slova."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:635
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use LC mode"
msgstr "Koristi LC mod"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:636
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this box is checked the cell reference shown at the left end of the "
"Formula Bar will be displayed in LC mode (i.e. L2C3) rather than in its "
"normal form B3. This does not seem to be of much use at the moment."
msgstr ""
"Ako je ova kućica popunjena, referenca ćelije lijevo od trake formule biće "
"prikazana u LC režimu, npr. L2C3 umjesto podrazumijevanog B3. Trenutno ne "
"izgleda da je ovo od neke koristi."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:642
#, no-c-format
msgid "Convert first letter to uppercase"
msgstr "Pretvori prvo slovo u veliko"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:643
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check this box and the first letter of any text you type in will "
"automatically be converted to uppercase."
msgstr ""
"Popunite li ovu kućicu, prvo slovo svakog teksta koji kucate biće pretvoreno "
"u veliko."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:648
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show grid"
msgstr "Prikaži mrežu"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:649
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If checked the grid (the cell limits) will be shown. This is default. If you "
"uncheck it, the grid will be hidden."
msgstr ""
"Ako je označeno linije (granice ćelije) će biti prikazane. Ovo je zadano. "
"Ako nije označeno, linije će biti sakrivene."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:654
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show page borders"
msgstr "Pokaži okvir stranice"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:655
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you check this option, the page borders will be drawn on your current "
"sheet. Per default the page borders are not displayed. It is useful to see "
"the page borders if you want to print your sheet."
msgstr ""
"Ako uključite ovu opciju, ivice strane će biti iscrtane na tekućem listu. "
"Podrazumijevano one nisu prikazane. Vidjeti ivice strane je korisno kada "
"želite da štampate list."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:661
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show formula"
msgstr "Prikaži formulu"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:662
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this box is checked &sheets; will display the actual formulae in cells "
"rather than the results."
msgstr ""
"Ako je ovo označeno &sheets; će prikazati stvarnu formulu u ćeliji umjesto "
"rezultata."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:667
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show formula indicator"
msgstr "Pokaži indikator formule"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:668
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this box is checked &sheets; will display a small blue triangle at the "
"bottom left corner of cells containing formulae. This is useful if you want "
"to protect cells with formulae."
msgstr ""
"Ako je ovo označeno  &sheets; će prikazati mali plavi trougao na dnu lijevog "
"ugla ćelija koje sadrže formule. Ovo je korisno ako želite zaštititi ćelije "
"sa formulama."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: format.docbook:674
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show comment indicator"
msgstr "Pokaži indikator komentara"

#. Tag: para
#: format.docbook:675
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this box is checked cells containing comments will be marked by a small "
"red triangle at the top right corner."
msgstr ""
"Ako je ova kućica popunjena, ćelije koje sadrže komentare biće označene "
"malim crvenim trouglom u gornjem desnom uglu."
